column1: # Title: Groundwater nonrenewable resource curves with capital costs disaggregated from electricity (pumping) requirements. Includes both energy and nonenergy costs
# Comments: Costs and depth bins are processed from superwell output. elec_coef = electric_energy / (Well_Yield * Annual_Operation_time))
# Source: Superwell model: https://github.com/JGCRI/superwell v0 (2020 runs)
# Units: costs in 1975USD per m3; available in km3; elec_coef in kwh per m3; depletion limits in percent
